How to use Selector?

 If you are not compiling it just create a config file called "selector.cfg" and put it in the same folder that selector exe.
 The config file format is: 
	rom_dir=roms/ <rom directory, IMPORTANT!!! put / after the folder name>
	extension=.ws <rom extension, IMPORTANT!!! put . before the extension>
	extension=.wsc
	emulator=ws <emulator name>
 It can support two types of extensions (for the moment). If your emulator only runs one kind of files (i.e. just .zip) 
 please put two times the same extension or it will crash.

 You can change images but you MUST keep vieju-splash.png and be carefull with image resolutions (take a look at images provided).
 
